deck: School bully who brutally attacked Robyn Hood and gave her the scar at her left eye.
description:
Origin

Cal's father, Oswald King, was a ruthless man. He raised his son Cal to have no empathy for others. As a result, Cal grew up being a psychotic bully. He once raped and scarred Robin Locksley, who later became Robyn Hood. As Robyn Hood, she exacted her revenge by pinning Cal down with her arrows and setting the place around him on fire.

Cal survived the attack and was healed by Avella and Sir Guy Of Gisbourne. He then took on the role of Sheriff of Nottingham.
name: Cal King

deck: Father of Cal King. He has his hands full with keeping his psychotic son in line.
description:
Origin

Oswald King was a ruthless man. He raised his son Cal to have no empathy for others. As a result, Cal grew up being a psychotic bully, who stabbed, maimed and raped others. Robyn Hood, a victim of her son, exacted her revenge by snapping Oswald's neck.
name: Oswald King
